{"tid":448464,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人d兄弟姐妹一返到屋企就會好膠？","createTime":"2017-10-26T08:47:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T09:04:16.000Z","uid":45055,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f5fa792c91da6dd38f48e2bf495047d2e8bfb6c3","tid":448464,"uid":45055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T08:47:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平時係見佢地同d朋友相處都幾正常<br />\n人緣仲叫幾好<br />\n但其實有個一返到屋企就會除左恤衫既兩個袖話自己佐助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一個就成日背廣告台詞，仲要我接住講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係咪得我屋企係咁？"},{"pid":"39b51a4a6b0696ce0f87b2ea83e14e6f8daafe63","tid":448464,"uid":63362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T08:49:33.000Z","msg":"我屋企都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咁講膠野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63f6c432c737d9a246ac8469a0dbc321888beaf1","tid":448464,"uid":45055,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T08:50:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我屋企都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咁講膠野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實點解會咁<br />\n佢地d fd上黎屋企玩個時佢地唔係咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e14940cd52e69ecb4ae15ba497eb76e776ee443","tid":448464,"uid":94090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T08:53:07.000Z","msg":"喺最親既人面前露出真我"},{"pid":"626f4184ea29ded9fc6075ba7765